| VisualFeedbackLearner | VisualFeedbackLearner | WireCrossLearningSubscriptions() |
| VisualWorkflowComposer | VisualWorkflowComposer | WireCrossLearningSubscriptions() |
| KnowledgeCodeTemplateStore | KnowledgeCodeTemplateStore | WireCrossLearningSubscriptions() |
