### Event Flow Map (Bidirectional)

| Event | Publisher | Subscribers |
|---|---|---|
| codegen_success | DynamicCodeSkill, LearningCortex, PatternLearning | LearningCortex, CodePatternLearning, CodeGenLibrary, DynamicCodeExamples, DynamicGlossary, FewShotLearning, KnowledgeCodeTemplateStore, RecipeStore, CodeAutoFixer (via sync) |
| codegen_failure | DynamicCodeSkill, LearningCortex | LearningCortex, CodePatternLearning, CodeGenLibrary, FailureRecoveryLearner |
| skill_failure | AgentOrchestrator | LearningCortex → FailureRecoveryLearner, VisualFeedbackLearner |
| skill_recovery | AgentOrchestrator, FailureRecoveryLearner | LearningCortex (correlator + tracker), VisualFeedbackLearner |
| skill_registered | DynamicCodeSkill | SkillKnowledgeIndex (re-index) |
| plan_completed | AgentOrchestrator | LearningCortex, ContextUsageTracker, CompositeSkillEngine, RecipeStore, ImprovementStore, InteractionRecorder, VisualWorkflowComposer |
| composite_discovered | CompositeSkillEngine, SelfTrainingScheduler | SkillKnowledgeIndex (re-index) |
| knowledge_indexed | SelfTrainingScheduler | KnowledgeCodeTemplateStore |
| context_used | ContextUsageTracker | ContextWindowOptimizer |
| glossary_updated | DynamicGlossary | (available for future subscribers) |
| pattern_learned | ImprovementStore | (available for future subscribers) |

### Validation

- `SelfTrainingScheduler.RunHubValidation()` chạy mỗi cycle để kiểm tra missing dependencies
- `LearningModuleHub.GetDependencyGraph()` xuất sơ đồ dependency cho debugging
- `LearningModuleHub.ValidateConnections()` trả về danh sách issues nếu có module bị thiếu dependency

### Nguyên tắc

- **Không cô lập**: Mọi module PHẢI register vào `LearningModuleHub`
- **Event-driven**: Giao tiếp giữa modules qua events, không gọi trực tiếp
- **Verify tích hợp**: Trace `WebViewBridge.Initialize()` đảm bảo component mới được wire
- **Persistence**: Mọi learning data phải persist qua `SelfLearningPersistenceManager`
- **Idle learning**: `SelfTrainingScheduler` tự động phát hiện và tích hợp trong cycle tiếp theo
- **CrossSkillCorrelator persistence**: Correlation data persist qua file, không mất khi restart
